feat: play / join game:
  - ways to start a game:
    - play (create a room): 
      - creates a room
      - user configure room options
      - user wait for player if room is public
      - if user hits play, empty space is filled by bots (bots will be added later)

    - join public room:
      - user sees a list of public rooms
      - user can join any of the public rooms
      - user waits for room creator to start the game

    - join private room:
      - user enters the room id
      - user joins the room
      - user waits for room creator to start the game

    - impelementation:
      - three screen setup:
        1. home screen
        2. lobby screen
        3. game screen

      - home screen:
        - four panels:
          - name input panel:
            - expects a name
            - stores in local storage
          - create room panel
            - exepcte nothing
          - join public room panel
            - expectes a choice of public rooms
          - join private room panel
            - expectes a room id

      - lobby screen:
        - two panels:
          - joined player list
            - shows a list of players
            - leave game
            - start game 
          - room configuration (read/write for creator readonly for players)
            - public / private
            - joining link
